Coffee

Finding coffee shops in Hobart is not too difficult, here’s my favourites:

  • Criterion Street Cafe
  • Villino Specialty Coffee on Criterion
  • Ecru Coffee on Criterion
  • Pigeon Hole on Goulburn
  • Parklane Espresso in Salamanca
  • Pollen Tea on Hampden
  • Machine Laundry Cafe in Salamanca (as the name imply, it’s also a laundry over there…)

Food & Beer

  • Preachers on James
  • The Den in Salamanca
  • Hobart Brewing Company: Inside/Outside Seating
  • Whiskey in Salamanca
  • Ti Ama in Salamanca (Wood-hoven pizza)
  • Magic Curries on Hampden (Indian)
  • For SeaFood: all around the Warf

Pharmacy/Chemist: My Chemist in Salamanca

Sim Card: Vodaphone, on Elizabeth (30$ for 35GB of data + unlimited call in Australia + limited time international).
